    Syntax
    [ExecuteInEditMode]
[RequireComponent(typeof(CanvasRenderer), typeof(RectTransform))]
[DisallowMultipleComponent]
[AddComponentMenu("Spine/SkeletonGraphic (Unity UI Canvas)")]
public class SkeletonGraphic : MaskableGraphic, ICanvasElement, IClippable, IMaskable, IMaterialModifier, ISkeletonComponent, IAnimationStateComponent, ISkeletonAnimation, IHasSkeletonDataAsset
